{"type": "article", "id": 59627, "title": "ASICS Tiger 代言找来新生代演员，欧珑香水发布气味电台| 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2018-12-24T04:50:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 46177, "name": "2018"}, {"id": 55367, "name": "ASICS Tiger"}, {"id": 1977, "name": "豆瓣"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181224122400V9EoyCOXium15LJj.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"UulA\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4319605226671756?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宋威龙成为 ASICS Tiger 大中华区品牌代言人。</b></a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181224122429hbEQtfAJvqwCuF6r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"PFpw\">统一阿萨姆奶茶联合 Discovery 探索频道和小米，<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4319242843579971?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>推出限量款“探索好心情”音乐杯，</b></a>喝一口奶茶切换一首音乐。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181224122918QwAlXp0gYWMSECsT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z0816mj3cgk\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>值得一看的Case</h3><p><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4320351771074992?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google×肯德基“猜画小歌送心愿”主题店，</b></a>已于上海肯德基曼克顿店正式开张，这次画的是炸鸡美食。该活动将于 12 月 31 日截止。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812241229442tqgY14UdVOnMTcb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812241229451CpzNlXsFfZVUoib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812241229466AMDyqctGdx0KISa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812241229448VvHyTQ15DJ9CxjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"W8LE\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4320345182406652?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>欧珑香水“气味电台”第二集发布，</b></a>片中周杰伦雪夜驱车，去见爱人一面。第二集的香水之前名为“西柚天堂”，调整成了“情柚独钟”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=v0817hgh2ju\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"OrdD\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4319742296620928?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>香奈儿 J12 最近和姜思达工作室上线影片“我想要”，</b></a>片中姜思达与马思纯、陈粒、蒋方舟和范湉湉对话，分别用 “54321” 不同字数的词语来阐述自己人生的关键词。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=n0816o4fc0y\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"JRtL\">家居设计品牌 ziinlife 吱音发布 5 周年品牌广告片“有趣的家具，懂你的设计”，选取了几个戏剧性的场景来展现吱音家居的设计和功能，凸显品牌的创意性。同时通过短片回答了“吱音是谁”。由创意工作室 RED+PLUS 制作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0777y5jl9m\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0530yfqpbx\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b0779pi0ei8\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0779vw1vj9\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0766f6xfk2\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"2NUx\" class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://t.jimingkeji.com.cn/ctrip-db1215/home/index/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">豆瓣和携程联合推出“前往电影中的旅行栖息地” H5</a>，</b>在豆瓣发布的 2018 年度电影榜单内设置了 H5 入口，其中埋藏了今年榜单电影中的彩蛋。用户选择台词来作答，生成属于自己的旅行栖息地。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181224123217MylAzj9REx8e3WqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.604000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181224123218mG6nV8rN7IjHqQyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.604000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"XOlb\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/oreo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥利奥在 Twitter 上发布了多支圣诞颂歌短片，</b></a>并向汉堡王、Wendy’s、Buzzfeed、乃至 Twitter 等 6 个品牌喊话，希望转发来宣传节日气氛。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=e0817d2v2n3\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Unsplash@<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@scherbakovx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anton Scherbakov</a></p>"}